              ->  Hash  (cost=29.98..29.98 rows=1198 width=10) (actual time=0.131..0.131 rows=599 loops=1)
                     Buckets: 4096  Batches: 2  Memory Usage: 47kB
                    ->  Seq Scan on customer c  (cost=0.00..29.98 rows=1198 width=10) (actual time=0.001..0.055 rows=599 loops=1)
        ->  Hash  (cost=75.81..75.81 rows=4581 width=8) (actual time=0.661..0.661 rows=4581 loops=1)
